    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, lets get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> chicken breast strips </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
