    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile,<strong> </strong>chop your<strong> waxy potatoes</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a heatproof bowl, then cover the bowl with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top with a fork</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 6-8 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p>",
