      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, add the <strong>cooked potatoes</strong> and <strong>chopped tomato</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>torn lettuce </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>balsamic tomato dressing </strong>(reserve the rest for later!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
