    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is nearly ready, add your <strong>pumpkin seeds </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until toasted and lightly golden – these are your <strong>toasted pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
