      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> cooked chicken </strong>and <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>over your <strong>dressed salad </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken caprese salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>balsamic tomato dressing </strong>and sprinkle with the <strong>toasted pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
